{"tid":1321263,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸穩維新聞黎料啦","createTime":"2019-07-15T15:25:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T01:28:01.000Z","uid":216002,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1f902d947fd6055748d795db29bc730fbf5cd1ec","tid":1321263,"uid":216002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:25:15.000Z","msg":"老豆不嬲藍絲黎嘅 但一直扮中立 仲講到自己好好人 比我地三姐妹遊行 比曬人情我地<br />\n<br />\n我呢幾日不斷係朋友圈發啲警察打人相 佢就不斷講警察點慘法  咁都算<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但係！佢竟然係朋友圈到發啲咁嘅野，真係好嬲！點解可以藍到個腦都有事</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/p0Z1iRiZ1omuctAFjB1GdA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2Fp0Z1iRiZ1omuctAFjB1GdA&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cC%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=4422472e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/p0Z1iRiZ1omuctAFjB1GdA</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文章嘅圖 就斷中指 但入面嘅圖 就係警比人咬斷相嘅圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要話有人用鉗鉗！大家一定要防止屋企嘅港豬廢老睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：比曬圖阿爸睇人地比人挖 緊張先咬到人咁 佢都覺人錯 上水跳橋事件 覺得係警察救返佢一命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經救唔返個廢老 如果有巴絲建議點樣令我老豆冇咁藍 不仿講一講"},{"pid":"39655fe14fcb369793f9ad03f3a880052f9f0c9d","tid":1321263,"uid":216002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:25:31.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"8c2317b0d9add56be18e7c72051d83ceeeb9b957","tid":1321263,"uid":260988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:27:39.000Z","msg":"總點應該係佢獲得消息嘅渠道"},{"pid":"6679fb0ec7c695e39ae5244c4c8beb52850000f2","tid":1321263,"uid":216002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:32:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"04dc937cff821e4742c75e9f44da1c5a26a83dc2","tid":1321263,"uid":182088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:35:06.000Z","msg":"呢篇我都收到"},{"pid":"6f5838bee96acd2308f6f9255da22b23f0bce08